latestPosts.caption:
I cried over this once. Not the brand, but what the no meant to me. I felt like I wasn’t good enough. But I didn’t quit. Today, the brand that once passed on me reached out again. If you’re in your ‘rejection’ phase, stay. The comeback feels soft and strong.

I just needed to share this tiny full-circle moment with you.
